<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Connect the intelligent tester to the DLC3.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Start the engine.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Select "DATA LIST" and read the value displayed on the intelligent tester (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000XHW00AX"/>).</ptxt>
